58 findings of said feasibility analysis to the Clerks of the House and Senate, the Joint Committee
59 on Transportation and the Joint Committee on Homeland Security and Public Safety not later
60 than six months following the passage of this Act.
61 SECTION 4. Sections 1 and 2 of this act shall take effect ninety days following the filing
